While an AE stun might be helpfull in some situations, I personally would mem something like that extremely rarely.<br>
<br>
I would LOVE to see ToK turned back into something that goes along the lines of the spells original intent.<br>
The best idea towards those lines I've seen at this point would be the Channeling debuff, Not soo much as to totally prevent casting. But one of those things that would at least give you a chance of interrupting that gating giant, Dragon(insert raid mob here).<br>
<br>
For those people asking for Giant/Dragon enabled stuns, I'm sorry guys but that ain't gonna happen.  These types of mobs are &quot;Totally&quot; immune to stun as per a race ability, making any one stun work on them not only defeats the purpose of this race ability, but would require a good amount of programming changes in respects to the race ability and the stun in question. <p>Click Sig for Magelo profile.<BR>
